77735e04dac713df63","tid":415923,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家遲左3日都未m come<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n媽媽唔好唔要我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57059435e2e91b9b7406dba1389485888cb5e27","tid":415923,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"晚晚都漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5969e193ce78b85d7b472b1a33a99c2644458aad","tid":415923,"uid":83597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb07679e19fc93732a87f5dffea9e358fbeea615","tid":415923,"uid":68728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先唔可以企直個人<br />\n一定要伏係到或者訓係到<br />\n企一定會暈（唔好問點解）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住臉色係蒼白無力，狂流汗💦<br />\n聽唔到野，只係聽到怪獸聲<br />\n個肚好痛好痛 以為自己就死<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆啦 如果留係屋企我都可以死係床到捱下訓下<br />\n但如果係返學返工時候真係比死更難受<br />\n最難受係其他人覺得難以置信<br />\n會質疑你有幾痛呀？真係好痛咩？<br />\n男仔，<span style=\"color: red;\">你地試過痛到唔想做男仔既痛未</span>？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 <br />\n<br />\n買樓 買車 <br />\n工作上位 <br />\n搵工女性優先<br />\n兩性差別對待"},{"pid":"b42ab368bd9c2dbb18cc885a28d644adf1f198a8","tid":415923,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"試過行行下突然起痛